Watch carefully, arms straight.

00:22:47.210 --> 00:22:51.320
Using the feet as points, the body is relaxed.

00:22:54.560 --> 00:23:00.580
So handsome. I feel like if he takes off his forensic scientist robe, it's all muscle underneath.

00:23:06.340 --> 00:23:09.050
I have a guess.

00:23:09.050 --> 00:23:11.600
What guess?

00:23:11.600 --> 00:23:15.740
He might have a criminal record.

00:23:44.260 --> 00:23:47.760
32 seconds, not bad.

00:23:49.910 --> 00:23:53.790
Now, we'll start today's official training.

00:23:55.780 --> 00:23:59.860
Fanzhou, are you going home for Independence Day?

00:23:59.860 --> 00:24:01.280
We can go back together.

00:24:01.280 --> 00:24:03.480
I'm not going back.

00:24:03.480 --> 00:24:05.450
But Auntie...

00:24:09.360 --> 00:24:14.230
I'm so tired. Once I think about how we have to do frog jumps this afternoon, I just want to bite off my tongue and die.

00:24:14.230 --> 00:24:17.580
