00:24:17.580 --> 00:24:19.210
- Thanks. <br> - Who's coming after your soul?<br><i>(T/N: It can also mean someone caught her interest)</i>

00:24:19.210 --> 00:24:22.050
- Are you that bored?<br>- You're here.

00:24:25.110 --> 00:24:27.050
You two are too much! You didn't even wait for me to eat.

00:24:27.050 --> 00:24:29.600
You didn't even get your food, don't you feel embarrassed?

00:24:30.630 --> 00:24:34.150
Hello, I'm Cai Yasi. A buddy of Zhou Xiao.

00:24:34.150 --> 00:24:37.620
Hello, I'm Luo Wei. Zhou Xiao's dormmate.

00:24:38.600 --> 00:24:40.460
Dormmate.

00:24:40.460 --> 00:24:42.560
Zhou Xiao must've caused a lot of trouble for you guys.

00:24:42.560 --> 00:24:44.660
Her brain is a bit weird.

00:24:44.660 --> 00:24:48.090
Her reflexes are very slow so please excuse her.

00:24:48.090 --> 00:24:49.950
Who are you talking about?

00:24:49.950 --> 00:24:52.930
Who is the one that keeps buying game accessories and tries to get free food from friends?

00:24:52.930 --> 00:24:55.720
What a coincidence, you really didn't eat.

00:24:55.720 --> 00:24:57.390
I forgot. I forgot.

00:24:57.390 --> 00:25:00.150
Sorry, there's a backup.

00:25:01.570 --> 00:25:06.740
All right, Zhou Xiao. You dare talk to me this way? You're done for.

00:25:06.740 --> 00:25:07.890
What are you doing?

00:25:07.890 --> 00:25:10.190
Don't worry, just eat.

00:25:13.070 --> 00:25:15.520
- Don't look. <br>- You–

00:25:16.090 --> 00:25:17.930
Look.

00:25:19.540 --> 00:25:21.150
- What is it?<br> - Show me.

00:25:21.150 --> 00:25:23.540
It's big pig trotters!

00:25:27.810 --> 00:25:30.540
I need to go back to the lab. Take your time eating.

00:25:30.540 --> 00:25:32.300
I'm done, too.

00:25:32.300 --> 00:25:35.770
Stop looking! Don't zoom in on my nostrils.

00:25:36.800 --> 00:25:38.900
Don't zoom in.

00:25:42.280 --> 00:25:44.160
I already saw it.

00:25:45.560 --> 00:25:49.270
Whatever. You're not the only one.

00:25:50.080 --> 00:25:53.130
Stop talking to us randomly, thank you.

00:25:56.070 --> 00:25:57.310
Close it, close it.

00:25:57.310 --> 00:25:58.940
No.

00:26:04.890 --> 00:26:06.530
Who's she?

00:26:06.530 --> 00:26:11.580
She's our new student representative. I've seen her picture on our school's forum.

00:26:12.800 --> 00:26:14.490
Does she have a grudge against you?

00:26:14.490 --> 00:26:16.140
No.

00:26:18.070 --> 00:26:19.670
Delete it.

00:26:19.670 --> 00:26:21.460
It's fine. I have backups.

00:26:24.460 --> 00:26:26.720
Both eyes straight ahead.

00:26:26.720 --> 00:26:30.200
Don't waver. Stand!

00:26:34.590 --> 00:26:37.230
Student Zhu Lu, do you want to take a break?

00:26:37.230 --> 00:26:39.490
Instructor, no need.

00:26:40.730 --> 00:26:42.290
Squat!

00:26:46.680 --> 00:26:48.200
Stand!

00:26:53.660 --> 00:26:56.220
<i>[Huoxiang Zhengqi Shui] <br>(T/N: herbal medicine for heatstroke; contains alcohol)</i>

00:26:59.300 --> 00:27:02.630
Today's instructor was so mean. Frog jumps!

00:27:02.630 --> 00:27:05.230
- My legs aren't mines anymore. <br>- Yeah.

00:27:08.310 --> 00:27:10.290
I have an idea.

00:27:17.020 --> 00:27:20.960
- Thanks.<br>- Take revenge for me.

00:27:20.960 --> 00:27:22.780
Here, try it.

00:27:24.330 --> 00:27:26.730
- How is it? <br> - It's like I'm stepping on clouds.

00:27:26.730 --> 00:27:29.830
- How awesome! I want some!<br>- I want some, too.

00:27:29.830 --> 00:27:30.950
¥5 for one.

00:27:30.950 --> 00:27:32.180
So noisy!

00:27:32.180 --> 00:27:35.620
Can you guys be quiet? It's so noisy!

00:27:35.620 --> 00:27:38.150
So what that we're noisy for a bit?

00:27:38.150 --> 00:27:40.290
Zhu Lu, we've endured you for a really long time!

00:27:40.290 --> 00:27:43.870
You're always so mean every day! Why should we endure it?

00:27:44.970 --> 00:27:48.910
Because I'm your dormmate and you guys don't like me!

00:27:52.430 --> 00:27:54.450
Are we that obvious?

00:27:55.260 --> 00:27:57.590
You guys all exclude me.

00:27:59.350 --> 00:28:03.430
I want to change dorms. I'm going to change you all!

00:28:03.430 --> 00:28:05.950
Fine, then go tell the Dorm Manager Auntie to change.

00:28:05.950 --> 00:28:08.530
- I'm not going!<br>- Fine, then I'll go.

00:28:08.530 --> 00:28:11.190
Wait, wait!

00:28:11.190 --> 00:28:15.510
I think something's wrong. Let me go see.

00:28:21.150 --> 00:28:24.100
Zhu Lu?

00:28:25.230 --> 00:28:28.220
Do you know who you are?

00:28:30.200 --> 00:28:32.690
Zhu Lu...

00:28:33.430 --> 00:28:34.720
Who's that?

00:28:34.720 --> 00:28:40.370
Zhu Lu... Is it a Xiao Lu (small deer)?

00:28:44.930 --> 00:28:46.660
Do you know who I am?

00:28:46.660 --> 00:28:49.500
- Be careful, be careful. <br>- I'm a small deer!

00:28:49.500 --> 00:28:53.940
- Yeah, yeah, you're a small deer.<br>- Be careful! There's a step.

00:28:56.670 --> 00:28:59.310
Let's go, my mount.

00:28:59.310 --> 00:29:00.960
Let's go.

00:29:00.960 --> 00:29:02.700
Hurry up!

00:29:02.700 --> 00:29:04.590
Let's go. Hurry.

00:29:04.590 --> 00:29:08.400
My feet hurt!

00:29:08.400 --> 00:29:10.940
Here.

00:29:10.940 --> 00:29:13.230
What's wrong with her?

00:29:13.230 --> 00:29:15.920
What kind of shock is she in?

00:29:17.500 --> 00:29:20.950
Is it because I was too mean scolding her earlier?

00:29:20.950 --> 00:29:26.580
From what I've noticed, she was weird before you guys started fighting.

00:29:26.580 --> 00:29:28.270
Then, what's wrong with her?

00:29:28.270 --> 00:29:32.760
She kept saying she's a small deer earlier.

00:29:34.610 --> 00:29:37.690
- Doctor. <br>- Doctor, how's my dormmate?

00:29:37.690 --> 00:29:40.010
These are her lab results.

00:29:40.620 --> 00:29:44.420
Nothing serious, she's just drunk.

00:29:44.420 --> 00:29:48.430
We're in military training every day, how do we have time to go drinking?

00:29:48.430 --> 00:29:49.970
I've looked at her medical records.

00:29:49.970 --> 00:29:55.000
She was prescribed a box of Huoxiang Zhengqi Shui yesterday at the hospital. Did she drink it?

00:29:55.000 --> 00:29:59.690
Yes, I saw her drink it yesterday.

00:29:59.690 --> 00:30:03.420
Then she got drunk from drinking Huoxiang Zhengqi Shui.

00:30:03.420 --> 00:30:06.600
It's fine. She can leave once she wakes up.

00:30:06.600 --> 00:30:08.760
- Thank you. <br> - You guys can take care of her.

00:30:08.760 --> 00:30:11.220
Thank you.

00:30:12.600 --> 00:30:17.660
You can get drunk from Huoxiang Zhengqi Shui? That's impressive!

00:30:22.560 --> 00:30:24.730
Scared me to death.

00:30:27.790 --> 00:30:30.930
<i>[Campus Hospital]</i>

00:30:50.000 --> 00:30:51.470
<i>Who's this?</i>

00:30:51.470 --> 00:30:54.620
<i>- Here's another one.<br>- Xiao Lu!</i>

00:30:54.620 --> 00:30:58.030
<i>- Xiao Lu!<br>- Wei-wei!</i>

00:31:04.020 --> 00:31:06.470
Wei-wei! Wei-wei.

00:31:06.470 --> 00:31:10.500
Go check. I think Xiao Lu is awake.

00:31:11.400 --> 00:31:15.170
- What did you just call her? <br> - Xiao Lu.

00:31:15.170 --> 00:31:19.900
Who is Zhu Lu? Is Zhu Lu a Xiao Lu (small deer)?

00:31:19.900 --> 00:31:22.240
Do you want to die, calling her that?

00:31:22.240 --> 00:31:26.760
Her ice-cold demeanor has completely cracked.

00:31:26.760 --> 00:31:28.560
I'm not scared of her anymore.

00:31:28.560 --> 00:31:31.020
She's awake.

00:31:39.750 --> 00:31:41.550
Are you okay?

00:31:51.110 --> 00:31:54.890
Where am I?

00:31:54.890 --> 00:31:58.760
The doctor said you got drunk from drinking Huoxiang Zhengqi Shui.

00:32:00.270 --> 00:32:03.260
I didn't cause trouble for you guys, did I?

00:32:04.060 --> 00:32:06.770
You really don't remember anything?

00:32:08.330 --> 00:32:10.250
No.

00:32:11.520 --> 00:32:13.220
It's not much trouble.

00:32:13.220 --> 00:32:17.440
Just that you got drunk and kept taking off your clothes, we couldn't stop–

00:32:17.440 --> 00:32:22.420
When did I do that? I just... grabbed your hair...

00:32:22.420 --> 00:32:24.810
Didn't you say you didn't remember?

00:32:24.810 --> 00:32:27.760
- Xiao Lu.<br>- Xiao Lu.

00:32:30.280 --> 00:32:32.600
You guys are so annoying.

00:32:45.700 --> 00:32:47.540
Eyes right.

00:32:47.540 --> 00:32:50.670
Ready, front. Goose-step.

00:32:50.670 --> 00:32:52.170
1!

00:33:05.750 --> 00:33:07.860
Gua-gua.<br><i>(frog sound)</i>

00:33:09.190 --> 00:33:11.000
Gua-gua.

00:33:12.610 --> 00:33:16.300
Gua-gua.

00:33:16.300 --> 00:33:17.760
Gua-gua.

00:33:17.760 --> 00:33:22.420
Student Tao Ling, what's "gua-gua"? Is a frog jump done by your mouth?

00:33:22.420 --> 00:33:25.250
Instructor, it's so tiring.

00:33:25.250 --> 00:33:28.050
If I don't find anything fun to do, I can't jump anymore.

00:33:28.050 --> 00:33:31.280
Gua-gua, gua-gua.

00:33:31.280 --> 00:33:36.030
You have good speaking skills. Too bad military training tests your endurance, not your public speaking.

00:33:36.030 --> 00:33:39.140
Student Zhou Xia is more serious than you.

00:33:40.350 --> 00:33:44.780
Instructor, I'm not being serious. I'm...

00:33:44.780 --> 00:33:48.490
too tired to do it with her.

00:33:52.740 --> 00:33:54.250
Gua-gua.

00:33:54.250 --> 00:33:57.650
Okay. You can rest.

00:33:59.960 --> 00:34:04.390
I used my body to defend everyone's resting time.

00:34:04.390 --> 00:34:07.930
Rest for 10 minutes, and then jump another 100 meters.

00:34:09.400 --> 00:34:13.570
Instructor, you're too merciless!

00:34:30.770 --> 00:34:33.250
You're up?

00:34:38.790 --> 00:34:42.980
Are you up, too?

00:34:43.000 --> 00:34:44.700
It hurts!

00:34:59.290 --> 00:35:00.930
What are you guys doing?

00:35:00.930 --> 00:35:03.160
Leg hurts.

00:35:03.160 --> 00:35:05.330
That much?

00:35:05.330 --> 00:35:09.870
Our instructor had us do frog jumps for 300 meters.

00:35:10.530 --> 00:35:12.480
This is the accumulation of lactic acid after exercise.

00:35:12.480 --> 00:35:17.220
Don't worry. Continue the military training and it'll turn the lactic acid into nothing.

00:35:17.220 --> 00:35:22.540
Student Xiao Lu, please put away that face of rejoicing toward other people's misfortune.

00:35:22.540 --> 00:35:24.170
Advance.

00:35:24.830 --> 00:35:27.050
Don't come any closer.

00:35:28.850 --> 00:35:33.980
- My ankle, right there.<br>- It hurts here.

00:35:33.980 --> 00:35:36.240
This big?

00:35:37.950 --> 00:35:40.040
Xiao Lu! My ankle, my ankle.

00:35:40.040 --> 00:35:42.850
Up, up. Yes, yes.

00:35:42.850 --> 00:35:46.080
And here, my knee.

00:35:46.080 --> 00:35:49.660
My knee, my knee.

00:35:58.530 --> 00:36:00.500
My god.

00:36:03.690 --> 00:36:05.550
Endure it.

00:36:06.390 --> 00:36:08.280
Good luck.

00:36:10.610 --> 00:36:12.460
Zhou Xiao!

00:36:18.460 --> 00:36:22.300
- What's wrong? <br> - Cai Yasi, pick that up.

00:36:23.720 --> 00:36:26.750
Fine, why are you so mean?

00:36:37.980 --> 00:36:43.430
Zhou Xiao, you're impressive now. You dare talk to me in this way.

00:36:46.200 --> 00:36:50.920
Bro, my leg hurts and I can't bend down!

00:36:52.820 --> 00:36:58.460
Do you know why this happened? It's because you don't get enough exercise. You know?

00:36:58.460 --> 00:37:00.480
I don't know. Give it to me.

00:37:00.480 --> 00:37:03.050
So you have to try harder!

00:37:06.740 --> 00:37:08.520
Good luck.

00:37:10.360 --> 00:37:16.180
Cai Yasi, once I'm better. I'll smash you into the wall that you can't even be peeled off!

00:37:51.210 --> 00:37:55.020
Student Zhao Fanzhou, well...

00:37:55.020 --> 00:37:58.000
can you pick up my hat for me?

00:38:01.500 --> 00:38:03.540
Are you sure?

00:38:11.100 --> 00:38:15.160
It's fine! I'll do it myself. You can go on your way.

00:38:44.870 --> 00:38:46.620
Thank you.

00:38:46.620 --> 00:38:48.570
No problem.

00:38:56.230 --> 00:38:58.630
He just smiled at me.

00:39:03.450 --> 00:39:05.810
Why did he smile at me?

00:39:08.580 --> 00:39:10.900
I'm so scared.

00:39:12.330 --> 00:39:14.450
Psycho.

00:39:19.680 --> 00:39:21.630
At ease.

00:39:21.630 --> 00:39:26.570
Today is the last day of military training. I hope everyone gets energized

00:39:26.570 --> 00:39:29.140
and finishes off this last line of duty. In the morning,

00:39:29.140 --> 00:39:33.830
we'll conduct a wireless real combat drill. This afternoon will be the concluding ceremony.

00:39:33.830 --> 00:39:37.680
And then, this year's military training will be over!

00:39:37.680 --> 00:39:41.600
Yes!

00:39:41.600 --> 00:39:45.070
<i>Freshmen, the activity area will be in the hill behind the school.</i>

00:39:45.070 --> 00:39:48.370
<i>Five people per group. Eight groups total, each will be given 30 minutes.</i>

00:39:48.370 --> 00:39:51.130
<i>In 30 minutes, those who don't find the hidden transmitter</i>

00:39:51.130 --> 00:39:54.150
<i>will be counted as a fail. Half your military training credits will be deducted.</i>

00:39:54.150 --> 00:39:57.370
Instructor, everything is going well.

00:40:26.500 --> 00:40:28.600
Are you okay?

00:40:35.000 --> 00:40:36.150
What are you doing?

00:40:36.150 --> 00:40:38.320
Checking your injury.

00:40:39.300 --> 00:40:43.210
I just fell. It's not that serious.

