Injuries to the head can lead to concussions or bleeding in the brain.

00:40:48.760 --> 00:40:53.710
Clinical display as Retrograde amnesia. Temporarily loss of consciousness and headache,

00:40:53.710 --> 00:40:59.040
nausea and vomiting are all possible. More severe cases can cause–

00:41:01.650 --> 00:41:05.870
Then... can you please check for me immediately?

00:41:05.870 --> 00:41:08.240
Here.

00:41:12.190 --> 00:41:15.890
Say will "you heal what you eat" work?

00:41:16.970 --> 00:41:20.910
Right now, I really want to eat baked pig's brain.

00:41:22.790 --> 00:41:25.920
Don't laugh. Once you laugh, I get goosebumps.

00:41:25.920 --> 00:41:28.470
Am I okay?

00:41:28.470 --> 00:41:31.560
Let me check. Don't move.

00:41:31.560 --> 00:41:33.620
Be gentle.

00:41:35.920 --> 00:41:38.510
There.

00:41:38.510 --> 00:41:44.570
<i>Student Zhao Fanzhou, someone's injured at the hill's exit. Go check it out.</i>

00:41:44.570 --> 00:41:46.340
Roger.

00:41:48.700 --> 00:41:52.500
Didn't you say I have a concussion? Where are you going?

00:41:52.560 --> 00:41:54.540
You...

00:41:54.540 --> 00:41:56.490
You're fine.

00:42:05.520 --> 00:42:07.520
I'm fine?

00:42:17.480 --> 00:42:20.290
Why do you have two of those in your hands?

00:42:25.050 --> 00:42:28.140
Sorry, I thought you'd be able to catch it.

00:42:29.700 --> 00:42:33.310
This is your friend's. Give it back to her for me.

00:42:34.070 --> 00:42:36.660
Are you crazy?

00:42:44.480 --> 00:42:49.340
Isn't this mine? Why do you have it? It's broken.

00:42:50.200 --> 00:42:52.810
I didn't do it.

00:42:52.810 --> 00:42:56.240
Does the new student representative have a grudge against you?

00:42:57.090 --> 00:43:02.090
<i>Good afternoon. My name's Jia Yichun, and I'm a 2016 new student from the Psychology Department.</i>

00:43:02.090 --> 00:43:06.560
<i>I'm honored to give this speech as a representative of all the new students.</i>

00:43:06.560 --> 00:43:09.940
Sorry, I almost made you lose half of your credit.

00:43:09.940 --> 00:43:14.210
It's okay, at least we still found it at the end with Cai Yasi's help.

00:43:14.210 --> 00:43:16.940
A genius computer youth is truly brilliant.

00:43:16.940 --> 00:43:19.960
Yeah, the process isn't important, the result is.

00:43:19.960 --> 00:43:24.820
It has also enabled students to form a clear plan of their future college life.

00:43:24.820 --> 00:43:28.740
Look.

00:43:28.740 --> 00:43:31.130
This military training...

