Who did this?

00:43:46.160 --> 00:43:49.220
- I don't know.<br>- It's so cool.

00:43:57.070 --> 00:43:59.950
Xiao, what are you looking at?

00:43:59.950 --> 00:44:02.590
Nothing.

00:44:03.940 --> 00:44:07.230
<i>If it's not him, then who is it?</i>

00:44:14.120 --> 00:44:17.030
<i>[Preview]<br>Waiting for you who has literature accomplishments.</i>

00:44:17.030 --> 00:44:19.540
<i>I came to find the programming club about finding the hacker.</i>

00:44:19.540 --> 00:44:21.260
<i>I can help you investigate this hacker!</i>

00:44:21.260 --> 00:44:23.720
<i>I've already thought of how we're going to find the hacker.</i>

00:44:23.720 --> 00:44:26.220
<i>- They found the hacker!<br>- So, you really did it?</i>

00:44:26.220 --> 00:44:29.220
<i>It wasn't her. You've misunderstood.</i>

