♫ <i>Thank you for giving me a pure friendship</i> ♫

00:45:04.060 --> 00:45:08.210
♫ <i>You will also have a love that belongs solely to you</i> ♫

00:45:09.500 --> 00:45:17.300
♫ <i>I’m so fortunate to have you in my youth</i> ♫

